OL,5,G2100 Dave Allen: The Immaculate
OL,6,G     Selection
OL,7,     FAn anthology of Dave Allen's
OL,8,     Ffinest, funniest and most
OL,9,     Firreverent material, compiled from
OL,10,     Fhis time at the BBC from 1971 to
OL,11,     F1986.
OL,12,G2200 Dave Allen: God's Own Comedian
OL,13,     FReflecting on the career of the
OL,14,     Fman once described as Britain's
OL,15,     Fmost controversial comic.
OL,16,G2300 Dave Allen
OL,17,     FIrish stand-up comedian Dave Allen
OL,18,     Fentertains a studio audience with
OL,19,     Fhis unique wit, humour and
OL,20,     Fsatirical observations. First
OL,21,     Fbroadcast in 1990.
